"tag-al-fitnah","tag-hereafter-akhirah","tag-manners-adab","tag-monotheism-tawhid","tag-parables-amthal","tag-renewal-al-tajdid","tag-signs-of-the-hour","tag-trials-al-balaa"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-2W5","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":3721,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/18\/zakat-al-fitr-ramadan\/","url_meta":{"origin":11289,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Zakat al-Fitr at end of Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 18, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, obligated payment of charity at the end of Ramadan, a portion of dates or barley, upon slave and freeman, male and female, young and old among the Muslims. The Prophet ordered it to be given before people\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31942,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/10\/one-sa-food-zakat-al-fitr\/","url_meta":{"origin":11289,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: A portion of food due for Zakat al-Fitr","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 10, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: We would bring for Zakat al-Fitr a portion of food, or a portion of barley, or a portion of dates, or a portion of cheese, or a portion of raisins. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1506, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 985 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26036,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/03\/12\/prophet-full-stomach-khubz\/","url_meta":{"origin":11289,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Food: The Prophet never filled his stomach with bread","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 12, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, left this world while he had never ate to his fill of barley bread. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5098 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u062e\u064e\u0631\u064e\u062c\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25985,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/02\/26\/refined-processed-white-flour\/","url_meta":{"origin":11289,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Bread: Caution against refined, processed white flour","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 26, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Hazm reported: He asked Sahl, \u201cDid you see refined flour in the time of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him?\u201d Sahl said no. He said, \u201cWould you sift the barley flour?\u201d Sahl said, \u201cNo, but we would blow the husks from it.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5094 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5037,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/12\/prophet-dates-eid-al-fitr\/","url_meta":{"origin":11289,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Eid: The Prophet eats dates before Eid prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 12, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would not proceed on the day of Eid al-Fitr\u00a0until he had eaten some dates. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 953 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15071,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/15\/sunset-break-fast-maghrib\/","url_meta":{"origin":11289,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: Time to break fast at sunset, Maghrib","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 15, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Abi Awfa reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen you see the sun set and night has come from the east, it is time to break the fast.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1956, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1101 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/11289","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=11289"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/11289\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=11289"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=11289"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/t